{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8@1.pkg/1772602230855/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602231752", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8@1.pkg/1772602230855/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602231752"}, "identifier": "947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>【解析】C.有误，“寤寐思服”“辗转反侧”写出了男子追求女子时爱而不得时昼夜思念、忧思难眠的情形，而非愉快、喜悦的心境。</p>\n\n<p>【答案】C</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列对这首诗的理解，不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "下列对这首诗的理解，不正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8@1.pkg/item.json?v=1745482290900", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>全诗以“窈窕淑女，君子好逑”一句统领，表现了男子对所爱女子的爱慕和追求。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“流之”“采之”“芼之”写出了女子左右采摘荇菜时勤劳灵巧的姿态。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“寤寐思服”“辗转反侧”写出了男子追求女子时愉快、喜悦的心境和美好的幻想。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>本诗书写的爱情故事美好而不低俗，有苦恼而不悲戚，正符合孔子对诗经的评价“乐而不淫，哀而不伤”。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列对这首诗的理解，不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对这首诗的理解，不正确的一项是（　　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列对这首诗的理解，不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8@1.pkg/1772602230855/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602231752", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/947b5a39-22b7-40cb-a2f2-9f9267b64cd8@1.pkg/1772602230855/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=177